response.overview: For 25 years, the WWE Universe has come together every Monday night to witness the unpredictable, the unforgettable and the unstoppable action of the longest episodic television show in history, Raw! Emanating simultaneously from the original host site of the first episode of Raw, the Manhattan Center, and the Barclays Center in Brooklyn -- all your favorite Superstars from every generation of WWE come together to celebrate Raw 25!
response.title: WWE Raw 25th Anniversary
